      <title>随着降温迹象缓解美联储担忧，美元涨势放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/the-dollar-s-rally-falters-as-signs-of-cooling-ease-fed-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀压力的缓解增强了人们对美联储将在年底前开始降息的预期，美元将出现自去年 12 月以来的首次月度下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/the-dollar-s-rally-falters-as-signs-of-cooling-ease-fed-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 15:41:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴克莱表示，并购活动将继续保持两位数增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/double-digit-growth-in-m-a-activity-to-continue-says-barclays</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行表示，由于条件和乐观情绪有所改善，而且 2023 年非常平静，留下了许多被压抑的交易活动，明年并购交易应该会继续保持两位数增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/double-digit-growth-in-m-a-activity-to-continue-says-barclays</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 15:27:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油交易商预计 OPEC+ 维持当前供应限制的可能性为 70%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/oil-traders-see-70-chance-of-opec-holding-current-supply-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据芝加哥商品交易所集团 (CME Group) 的期权持仓情况，石油交易员认为 OPEC+ 在本周末会议上不改变当前减产措施的可能性约为 70%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/oil-traders-see-70-chance-of-opec-holding-current-supply-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 15:21:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 部长前往利雅得，会议地点再次改变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/opec-changes-meeting-venue-again-as-ministers-head-to-riyadh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据代表们透露，OPEC+ 将第二次更改 6 月会议地点，主要部长目前计划在利雅得亲自讨论石油政策。]]></description>
